<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-22 02:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5576 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-HKN-NHLNOTEBOOK-BOS &LR;      08-22 1815
