<P>
   NATION
</P>
<P>
   QUAKE-VICTIMS _ ATLANTA _ A report on the Mount Vernon Baptist
Church church service in Atlanta where the Kilic family, which lost
five members in the Turkish earthquake, worships. (Badie, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 12.
</P>
