<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-08-22 19:18 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5739 &Cx1f; tta-z
u i BC-FRANKENSTEIN-FOOD-ART     08-22 1039
