governments. The number of workers they employ _ everybody from
teachers to police officers to highway laborers _ rose 2 percent in
the year ending in March 1998, according to a recently released
report from the U.S. Census Bureau. By JOHN A. DVORAK. Story will
move in the ``a'' and ``f'' categories.
