comes in shades of gray. From silver cars to brushed-steel
refrigerators to gray clothes, cool colors are in. According to
color analysts, consumers are looking for high-tech colors that
evoke the coming century. By JOYCE SMITH. Story will move in the
``a'' and ``f'' categories.
