<SLUG> BC-FUTURE-COLOR-KAN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
COLOR CHOICE OF THE FUTURE? AMERICA'S GOING GRAY 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
