<HEADLINE>
NUMBER OF GOVERNMENT WORKERS ROSE 2 PERCENT IN YEAR ENDING IN MARCH
'98 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By JOHN A. DVORAK  
